  {"id":"30000000-0000-4000-8000-000000000003","name":"MDN Web Docs","slug":"mdn","url":"https://developer.mozilla.org/zh-CN/","description":"权威、系统的开放 Web 技术文档。","longDescription":"MDN Web Docs 是学习和查询 HTML、CSS、JavaScript 及浏览器 API 的核心参考资料。页面通常包含语法、示例、兼容性和规范链接，适合从入门学习到生产排障。中文页面方便快速理解，但遇到新标准或翻译滞后时，可以切换英文版本交叉核对。将 MDN 作为开发导航的基础入口，比依赖零散转载文章更容易获得准确且可追溯的信息。","logo":"","category":"development","tags":["free","developer","open-source"],"featured":true,"recommended":true,"sortOrder":30,"status":"published","pricing":"free","language":["zh-CN","en"],"screenshots":[],"alternatives":[],"relatedPosts":[],"createdAt":"2026-07-01T00:00:00+08:00","updatedAt":"2026-07-15T00:00:00+08:00","indexable":true},
