  {"id":"30000000-0000-4000-8000-000000000005","name":"Cloudflare","slug":"cloudflare","url":"https://www.cloudflare.com/zh-cn/","description":"DNS、CDN、安全防护与边缘网络服务平台。","longDescription":"Cloudflare 将 DNS、CDN、TLS、缓存和基础安全策略集中到一个控制台，适合管理分布在多台 VPS 上的个人站点。免费套餐已经能够覆盖常见的 DNS 托管、代理、证书和基础防护需求。使用时应将 SSL 模式设为 Full (Strict)，避免 Flexible 模式导致回源不加密；WordPress 登录、投稿接口和动态 API 不应套用静态页面缓存规则。Cloudflare 不是源站备份，仍需要独立的数据库与文件备份。","logo":"","category":"vps-ops","tags":["free","developer","china-friendly"],"featured":true,"recommended":true,"sortOrder":20,"status":"published","pricing":"freemium","language":["zh-CN","en"],"screenshots":[],"alternatives":[],"relatedPosts":["cloudflare-domain"],"createdAt":"2026-07-01T00:00:00+08:00","updatedAt":"2026-07-15T00:00:00+08:00","indexable":true},
